[ a                      owl:Axiom ;
  rdfs:comment           "ES: To study the induction of cell polarity in EMS, we used a genetic screen to identify recessive, maternal-effect, embryonic-lethal mutants in which both EMS daughters produces mesoderm, at the expense of endoderm. We identified 16 such mutations, defining 5 genes, mom-1\nthrough mom-5. " , "CS: E -> MS cell fate transformations in the C. elegans embryo are associated with defects in the Wnt signaling pathway." ;
  lego:evidence          :5716c41300000421 , :5716c41300000419 , :5716c41300000414 ;
